name: Monogatari
description:
LoRA trained on the anime adaptation of the monogatari series of ligh novels.

Trained on general tags but characters can be generated with associated tags

examples:

Tsubasa Hanekawa: 1girl, solo, long_hair, black_hair, hair_ornamen, brown_eyes, braid, glasses, hairclip, , twin_braids

Shinobu Oshino: 1girl, solo, long_hair, blonde_hair, yellow_eyes, blush_stickers

Mayoi Hachikuji: 1girl, solo, long_hair,, black_hair, red_eyes, ribbon, twintails, hair_ribbon, hairband

Hitagi Senjōgahara : 1girl, solo, long_hair,, blue_eyes, ponytail, purple_hair,

 

ect

if stuck on how to steer the characters inputting an example image into auto tagger will help.

This model was trained with labels constructed using smiling wolfs wd-v1-4-swinv2-tagger-v2 at .25 threshold. Tags outputted from that are likely to match the training data.

Suggested base model to use for the lora is 7th animeC
